{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cf0b846ab8","title":"中共中央关于梁漱溟所办勉仁学院处理办法给西南局的电报","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b2022ba93","index":0,"year":1950,"month":4,"day":5,"articleId":"cf0b846ab8"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ee42a388de","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于梁漱溟所办勉仁学院处理办法给西南局的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"cf0b846ab8"},{"id":"fa39b13c99","type":"appellation","text":"西南局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"cf0b846ab8"},{"id":"2d00ee2fba","type":"paragraph","text":"梁漱溟对其在北碚所办勉仁学院，提出两项办法：    一、请西南文教部主持，即将该院现有之教员、学生，归并于重庆各公立大学之相同学系内，该院即行停办。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"cf0b846ab8"},{"id":"2c8f706ef7","type":"paragraph","text":"二、现在该院学生既少，更有房舍、家具可让出，以供公用。除房舍系租借来者不必作价外，所有让出之家具，请政府作价收购，该院即以此项价款，贴补开支，勉强维持一期。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"cf0b846ab8"},{"id":"11c296831b","type":"paragraph","text":"以上两项办法，我们同小平商量以采第二办法较妥。请你们斟酌处理后电复。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"cf0b846ab8"},{"id":"df8d85fdff","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央四月五日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"cf0b846ab8"}],"page":{"id":"c3fed6800c","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"cf0b846ab8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}